    "description": "在这个花园里，各种美丽的植物绽放着她们的花朵。但是，这些植物还需要保护自己免受入侵，不然就会被入侵者捕食。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348190/extras/0ea5a72c0fd73c8a0b86e7b9361cda61.poster.avif?t=1684472364\" width=500 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348190/extras/0ea5a72c0fd73c8a0b86e7b9361cda61.webm?t=1684472364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348190/extras/0ea5a72c0fd73c8a0b86e7b9361cda61.mp4?t=1684472364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>为了保护花园植物，你需要扮演一名植物守卫，使用各种植物来抵御昆虫的侵袭。你可以选择种植不同种类的植物，每种植物都拥有自己的特殊技能和攻击方式。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348190/extras/51cf65fa64dbede2dc5eec323d0bd1a8.poster.avif?t=1684472364\" width=500 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348190/extras/51cf65fa64dbede2dc5eec323d0bd1a8.webm?t=1684472364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348190/extras/51cf65fa64dbede2dc5eec323d0bd1a8.mp4?t=1684472364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>但是，入侵者也不会坐以待毙，他们会利用各种方法向花园植物发起攻击。你需要时刻保持警惕，使用你的智慧和策略让植物们战胜入侵者，保卫花园的安宁。<br><br>通过不断的修建策略，逐步地升级繁荣的花园，你可以决定如何抵御来袭之敌。与时间赛跑，保卫自己和他人的花园，展现你的勇气和智慧！",
